Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.33,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running like a fugitive,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being chased by something
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.87,0:00:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside my heart is pounding
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My throat dry like it's withering
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.88,0:00:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For no single one,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To none does belong,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time is ours, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling the pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.09,0:00:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling our hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unraveling shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:00:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stifling our breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:00:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reaching for beyond,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.67,0:01:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tearing through the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.94,0:01:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fighting and in love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.58,0:01:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the distant light above,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we are on the way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rockin' my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I've overused\Nmy Sharingan…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:02:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really… It will be hard just to\Nmove for about a week…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be better if\Nyou didn't move for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.90,0:02:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Sensei's awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.88,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Sharingan is fantastic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it puts that much of a strain\Non your body, it may not be worth it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did take down\Na real powerful Ninja like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably don't need to\Nworry for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that kid with the mask...\NWhat was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was an ANBU black ops\Nfrom the Hidden Mist village.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mask that the elite\NNinja Tracking Unit wears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elite Ninja Tracking Unit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're commonly called the\N "fire extinguishing corps,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their duty is to erase all traces\Nthat a Ninja ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.55,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The body of the Ninja reveals\Na variety of things…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninjutsu secrets and Chakra characteristics\Nwhich permeate the Ninja of their village…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:03:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the composition of secret medicines\Nused on a Ninja's body…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For instance, if I were to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.23,0:03:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every secret about my Sharingan\Nwould be investigated thoroughly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in the worst case,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a danger that\Nmy entire Jutsu could be stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\NTracker Ninja are specialists
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that prevent village secrets\Nfrom leaking out
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.78,0:03:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by killing Rogue Ninja\Nwho've run away from their village,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and completely eliminating\Ntheir bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'll cut the mouth cloth\Nand have him spit up blood…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.43,0:03:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it…myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?\NYou've already come back to life…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, you really are rough…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't pull them out\Nso violently or you really will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan on keeping\Nthat shady-looking mask on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a relic from the past,\Nand it's been handy for trickery…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I hadn't rescued you,\Nyou certainly would have been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were going to put me\Ninto a state of apparent death,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you didn't need to aim for\Nthe secret opening on my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a nasty one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be helped…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I didn't want to mark up\Nyour immaculate  body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, I can aim more accurately\Non the point on the neck
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where there's not much muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be numb for about a week\Nand won't be able to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.87,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since you're Zabuza,\Nperhaps you'll soon be able to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so innocent, smart,\Nand untainted…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I like about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am, after all, still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fog has lifted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.56,0:05:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.30,0:05:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be alright the next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next time…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be able to see right\Nthrough the Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Forest of Chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.88,0:05:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Zabuza is dead…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.88,0:05:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this indescribable uneasiness…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it must mean something\Nvery important…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a feeling\NI've overlooked something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?! 					Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…so to continue my earlier story…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.73,0:05:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja trackers…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.80,0:05:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take care of the bodies of people they've\Nkilled, immediately and on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.61,0:06:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did that kid with\Nthe mask do with Zabuza?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That masked one\Ntook Zabuza away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he needed proof he'd killed Zabuza,\Nhe could simply have taken the head…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.79,0:06:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the question is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the weapon the Ninja tracker kid\Nused to kill Zabuza…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A regular Senbon…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right…it's impossible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you guys\Nbeen clamoring on and on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably that…\NZabuza is alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.88,0:06:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kakashi Sensei,\Nyou made sure that he was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, I did make sure…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, he was probably just in\Na state of near-death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Senbon that Tracker Ninja used has\Na very low ability to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless it hits a vital spot…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that was originally used\Nfor medical treatments
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,such as acupuncture therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja trackers know all about\Nthe structure of the human body…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.09,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,putting people into a state of apparent\Nnear-death is probably simple for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.36,0:07:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, he went to the trouble of\Ntaking Zabuza's corpse
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which was probably heavier\Nthan he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.90,0:07:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Second, he used a Senbon,\Na weapon with a low ability to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From these two factors,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that youth wasn't aiming to\Nkill Zabuza but to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you reading\Nway too much into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something seems fishy,\Nmake preparations before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also an iron clad rule\Nof the Shinobi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph… To hear that Zabuza\Nmay be alive and to be pleased…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, what do we do to make preparations\Nbefore it's too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able\Nto move for a while…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll assign you training!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute! Even with training,\N we're not gonna be that strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our opponent is a Ninja whom even you,\Nwith the Sharingan, had a tough fight with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.26,0:08:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it that saved me\Nduring my difficult battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.13,0:08:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've all quickly grown…\Nespecially Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've grown the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He clearly does seem somewhat\Nstronger than before, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.08,0:08:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you noticed, Kakashi Sensei!\NNow it's getting interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.32,0:09:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not interesting at all…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Inari!\NWhere've you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back…Grandpa…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inari, what sort of greeting is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the Ninja\Nwho escorted your grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.67,0:09:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's okay.\NRight, Inari?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, these guys will die…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way they can\Noppose Gato and win.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.02,0:09:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a super hero who's gonna become\Nan awesome Ninja
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,named Hokage in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it's Gato or\NChocolat or whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not worried\Nabout those guys, at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, a hero. That's ridiculous!\NThere's no such thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.04,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to die,\Nyou'd better hurry up and go home…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inari, where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea…\NI'll be looking at the sea…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat… I need to tell him\Na thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.81,0:10:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.04,0:10:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.04,0:11:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, now the training begins!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.97,0:11:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So…before that, let me again explain\NChakra power for a Ninja, from the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.32,0:11:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this point…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we know about that!\NChatora, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.06,0:11:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sakura...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Naruto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.89,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiresome, so I'll explain it simply!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chakra is energy that\Na Ninja needs when he uses a Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's made up of two energies:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.94,0:11:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1) Physical energy gathered together\Nfrom each and every cell in the body and
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2) Spiritual energy accumulated based\Non numerous trainings and experiences!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Jutsu wrings out and\Ncombines these two energies
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from within the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and this is called\N "combining the Chakra."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Chakra is activated\Nby forming hand "signs."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.60,0:12:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iruka Sensei really does\Nhave good students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever! I may not understand\Ndifficult explanations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.88,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll just learn it with my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto is absolutely right…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're already able to use Jutsu…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! All of you still haven't used\NChakra efficiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.42,0:12:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on and listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Sakura explained earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,combining Chakra means picking up\Nboth the physical and spiritual energies
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and mixing them together\Nwithin the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And of course the amount of each energy,\Nthe preparation of the energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.88,0:12:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,changes based on\Nthe Jutsu you want to activate…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you at present aren't\Nusing Chakra efficiently!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.45,0:12:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're able to combine\Na lot of Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you're not able to control it\Nin a balanced way
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the effectiveness of the Jutsu\Nnot only will be cut in half
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.29,0:13:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it may not even\Nbe activated at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasting energy will prevent you from\Nbattling for long periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are some of\Nthe weaknesses that can occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What should we do…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to learn to control\Nthe Chakra with your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult training that requires you\Nto put your life on the line to master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What will we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tree-climbing…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.59,0:13:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tree-climbing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.29,0:13:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not just simple tree-climbing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will climb\Nwithout using your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.06,0:13:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well! Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's climbing…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perpendicular to the tree\Nand with his feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So see, kind of like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus the Chakra on the bottoms of your feet\Nand make them stick to the tree trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.73,0:14:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use Chakra well,\N you can do things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does something like that\Nmake you strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the main point…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The aim of this training is\Nto accumulate
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the required amount of combined Chakra\Nto the required spot…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.22,0:14:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is surprisingly difficult\Neven for an expert Ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The amount of Chakra used\Nfor tree-climbing is very subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the bottoms of the feet are\Nthe most difficult place to gather Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! In other words,\Nif you master that control
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it will be possible to master\Nany Jutsu. In theory, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second aim is to maintain\Nthat combined Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.18,0:15:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja combine the most Chakra\Nduring battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under such situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"control" and "maintenance"\Nof Chakra becomes most difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, nothing's really gonna\Nhappen with me saying this and that…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to learn it with your bodies
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use that Kunai to put a mark\Nat the spot
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where you can climb up to\Nunder your own strength now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.24,0:15:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next make an effort to\Nput a mark further from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't good enough to\Nwalk up from the start,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so run and use your momentum\Nto get used to it… You got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This training is nothing!\NHah, it's too easy for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the man\Nwho's grown the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the talk…\NNow get to it. Try climbing any tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.67,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, so first I need to gather\Nthe Chakra on the bottoms of my feet…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.45,0:16:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!! Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think it'd be this difficult to\Nmaintain a constant amount of Chakra…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Chakra is too strong\Nyou get pushed back…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the Chakra is too weak,\Nthere's no sticking power and that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.68,0:16:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference between Naruto and Sasuke\Nseems about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.59,0:16:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it looks like the one with the best control\Nof the Chakra is Sakura, the girl…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Way to go, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect from\Nthe girl I set my sights on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.88,0:17:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it does sort of tick me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.51,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Sasuke to notice me…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this always happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not only does Sakura have\Nknowledge about Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,her control and stamina\Nare pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.16,0:17:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be the closest one to\Nbecoming a Hokage…unlike someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, the Uchiha Clan\Nisn't really that great…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.84,0:17:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasuke won't like me then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having said that… Naruto and Sasuke…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those two have an incredible amount\Nof Chakra hidden in them…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.82,0:17:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Sakura can't even match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this training goes well,\Nthis will become an asset to them…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.19,0:18:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! First I'll catch up to Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.73,0:18:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it... for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.77,0:18:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they do that,\Nit's just a waste…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.53,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.90,0:18:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you got beaten and\Nhad to come back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ninja from the Hidden Mist Village\Nlook like total weaklings!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even clean up after\Nyour subordinates,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you think you're a "demon"!\NDon't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:18:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they're drawing swords…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey… There's no need to stay silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch Zabuza\Nwith your dirty hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's gonna break…!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He moved…in an instant…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that…\NI'm ticked off!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.19,0:19:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose again next time…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remember that there'll be\Nno place for you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haku… Such unnecessary actions…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too early to take down\NGato right now…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.04,0:20:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we make trouble here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be pursued by them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must restrain ourselves for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.19,0:20:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.90,0:20:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhhhh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ou–ch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm totally worn out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much stamina\Ncan those two have?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Naruto isn't getting\Nany better at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll soon give up and\Nstart throwing a tantrum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.56,0:20:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! He sure is\Nan easy one to figure out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you give me some tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.87,0:21:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep it a secret from Sasuke!\NCome on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting stronger and stronger…\NHow strong will he get…?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate Naruto…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the amount of your dormant Chakra\Nis probably more than Sasuke's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.46,0:21:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's even more than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look forward to it… I really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.43,0:23:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Inari...\NHe was crying all by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was looking at the sea\Nand crying the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always crying all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.01,0:23:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.31,0:23:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened\Nthat made him so sad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.35,0:23:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:\N "The Land Where a Hero Once Lived"
